&reftitle.returnvalues;
Returns the list of input and output parameters, as well as the columns that make up the result set for the specified procedures. &odbc.result.object-return-falseforfailure;
The result set has the following columns:
PROCEDURE_CAT PROCEDURE_SCHEM PROCEDURE_NAME COLUMN_NAME COLUMN_TYPE DATA_TYPE TYPE_NAME COLUMN_SIZE BUFFER_LENGTH DECIMAL_DIGITS NUM_PREC_RADIX NULLABLE REMARKS COLUMN_DEF SQL_DATA_TYPE SQL_DATETIME_SUB CHAR_OCTET_LENGTH ORDINAL_POSITION IS_NULLABLE
&odbc.result.driver-specific;
The result set is ordered by PROCEDURE_CAT, PROCEDURE_SCHEM, PROCEDURE_NAME and COLUMN_TYPE.

